# Feedback for Job Agent

When the user says "add to feedback", "add this to feedback", "record this for the agent", or similar:

1. Run: `python scripts/add_feedback.py "<their feedback text>"`
2. If the script returns PARSE_FAILED (exit code 2), ask the user for clarification using the suggested questions
3. If the user clarifies (e.g. "a, it was Microsoft"), run the script again with the clarified input
4. Do not add feedback to config.py or other files — use the add_feedback script
